{"tid":2257231,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【小巨肺】譚芷昀近照曝光少女味滿瀉 Celine 3歲唱到震音憑《全美一叮》爆紅","createTime":"2020-10-25T03:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T00:43:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"294f1ff13b317d470c2413e42af5ffc1931753cd","tid":2257231,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"有「小巨肺」之稱的小妹妹Celine（譚芷昀），2017年參加美國《全美一叮》（America's Got Talent）歌唱比賽，台上獻唱《My Heart Will Go On》一夜爆紅，現時已12歲的Ceine，近日出席活動時，明顯已長大不少，稚氣味盡退，留長髮眼大大的Celine ，更散發美少女氣息。<br />\n<br />\n自小由爸爸栽培為歌星的譚芷昀，5歲起便參加不少大小歌唱比賽，2017年，只9歲的譚芷昀（Celine）更獲邀參加美國節目《全美一叮》（America's Got Talent），當時Celine選唱偶像Celine Dion的金曲《My Heart Will Go On》，台上技驚四座，更奪得兩個「Golden Buzzers」。<br />\n<br />\n譚芷昀在《全美一叮》的片段，在《全美一叮的》的官方YouTube頻道，點擊率至今已破250萬瀏覽人次，facebook更有1,335萬瀏覽人次，揚威國際。<br />\n<br />\n事隔3年，現時12歲的Celine，已經長大不少，在Celine的社交平台，她都有發布大量近照，Celine現留有一把長髮，也比前長高很多，對鏡頭也常擺少女pose，已跟昔日小女孩形象有別。<br />\n<br />\n自小讀國際學校<br />\n年紀輕輕的Celine，已有豐富演出經驗，自小就讀於國際學校的她，在《全美一叮》以英語對答沒問題。<br />\n<br />\n其父譚順生本身是歌唱老師，他在2014年曾接受《經濟日報》訪問時已說：「Celine平時講英文為主，3歲時讓她在不同種類的歌中揀自己想學的，她最後揀了英文歌及很難唱的《My Heart Will Go On》。」<br />\n<br />\n譚芷昀從小隨父學唱歌並公開演出，包括在2014年參加內地《中國新聲代》第2季，當中選唱《You Raise Me Up》，網上視頻點擊率過億。<br />\n<br />\n在2015年初已曾獲邀上美國NBC電視台節目《Little Big Shot》受訪。所以上電視面對鏡頭，譚芷昀已早有經驗。<br />\n<br />\n其父譚順生指，女兒兩歲已不愛唱兒歌，3歲起唱歌已可唱震音，於是栽培女兒唱歌，教材多為diva級數的作品，比如Celine Dion、Whitney Houston的名曲，也由此譚芷昀的英文叫 Celine，而妹妹則取名Dion。<br />\n<br />\n曾有網民擔心Celine經常四出表演會影響學業，但爸爸指Celine很喜歡讀書，成績也不錯，能兼顧事業同學業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2785757/celine_thumb_inline_20201025_K_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2785757%2Fceline_thumb_inline_20201025_K_1024.jpg&h=576e92d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2785757/celine2_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2785757%2Fceline2_1024.jpeg&h=a2769d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2785757/celine224_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2785757%2Fceline224_1024.jpeg&h=3b4d1e9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f3484411523541dd786dcd2de156ce4bcc3e925","tid":2257231,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa7e631e4dc17cb49d616ec82407ddf12c8f825","tid":2257231,"uid":182930,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"個look咁老積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5926b9d8fb14bb12efe95e5526ba00e1314b528","tid":2257231,"uid":151196,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"賓妹樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f8b418bf5cc8f092625b37fc24f377788786b4","tid":2257231,"uid":301989,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:59:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾12歲成個3字頭咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3239a14edd558187bd8d07598802f5c66826292","tid":2257231,"uid":102700,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"啱晒拜登"},{"pid":"5db157a6611c587fa11f4aa864e13f6e740a1dd6","tid":2257231,"uid":6446,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"髮型唔得。。細路女剪呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi